You're building The Overlap, a newsletter at the intersection of music, marketing, and AI. It's your story: built two 7-figure businesses (180K + 70K audiences), spoke at FunnelHackingLive to 5,000 people, lost it all, and now rebuilding from zero while learning AI.

The promise: Real expertise + honest struggle + actual tactics. No bullshit.

