The honest truth:

You were an insecure kid who found success
Maybe you overcompensated with confidence
Built $2M in revenue, got praised AND hated
Lost it all due to illness and bad decisions
Now you're broke, frustrated, figuring out who you actually are
But you still know things: direct response marketing, AI/tech, music business
Why it works: Not a redemption arc. Just real vulnerability + real expertise.

